data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. Welcome to this charming, move in ready 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom house located in the desirable Sea Pines neighborhood in Hudson. Now PRICED TO SELL! Featuring a spacious open floor plan and cathedral ceilings, this home offers a comfortable and inviting atmosphere for you. Step inside and be greeted by the bright and airy living area, perfect for entertaining guests or simply relaxing after a long day. The open layout seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, creating a cohesive space for all your needs. The kitchen is well-appointed with ample cabinet space and a convenient breakfast bar. One of the highlights of this home is the enclosed patio, providing a serene space to enjoy the beautiful Florida weather. Whether you want to sip your morning coffee or unwind with a book, this outdoor oasis is the perfect spot. There is plenty of grass space for pets to roam. This neighborhood offers an array of key features that make it truly special. Located just one door down from Woodland Park, you'll have easy access to green spaces and recreational activities. Additionally, Sun west Park is just a stone's throw away, offering endless opportunities for water sports and outdoor fun. For those who love boating, this neighborhood provides a private gated boat launch, ensuring easy access to the water. There is also a private gated park on the gulf, allowing you to enjoy the stunning coastal views and sunsets. Access to these amenities is available with an optional paid civic association annual fee, which also grants you membership to the wildlife/bird sanctuary. One of the unique aspects of this neighborhood is the allowance of golf carts on roadways, providing a convenient and eco-friendly mode of transportation to the parks. Best of all, there is no HOA in this community. Instead, it has been converted into a civic association that solely looks after the parks. The annual dues for the civic association are optional, giving you the flexibility to choose your level of involvement. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this wonderful house your new home which is also just a 10 minute drive to Hudson beach. Schedule a showing today and experience the best of living! Seller has a clean 4 point inspection dated 12/13/2023 that the buyer can use for insurance and save money on.
